quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  26,123,Achina Adi ŵakaaniile achimitenga
  26,124,"Ndema jaŵasalile nnongo n’jao Hudu kuti: “Ana ngankogopa?”"
  26,125,“Chisimu une kukwenu ni Ntenga jwakulupichika.”
  26,126,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,127,"“Soni ngangun’juga pa yalakweyi malipilo, nganigaŵatu malipilo gangu ikaŵeje kwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope.”"
  26,128,“Ana nkutaŵa pachikwesya palipose pakusalala nyumba syeleuleu mwamasanje (pagamba kusaka kulosya machili ngaŵa syagonamo)?”
  26,129,“Ni nkulitaŵila makome gamakulungwakulungwa nti chisawu tinnonjele?”
  26,130,“Soni ntite mpute ngondo nkasaputa mwakulikwesya.”
  26,131,“Basi mun’jogopani Allah ni kumbikanila une.”
  26,132,“Soni mun’jogopani Ajula jwampele ichindu (yambonembone) yankuimanyilila.”
  26,133,“Ampele ilango ni ŵanache.”
  26,134,“Kwisa soni migunda ni sulo syatutumule.”
  26,135,“Chisimu une ngun’jogopela ŵanganyammwe ilagasyo ya lisiku lyekulungwa.”
  26,136,"Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Yalumope kukwetu, n’jamuche kapena nkaŵa mwa akwamuka.”"
  26,137,“Nganiyiŵatu ayi (yatukutendayi) ikaŵeje nyendele ja ŵandu ŵandanda.”
  26,138,“Soni nganituŵatu uwwe ŵanti ni kupedwa ilagasyo.”
  26,139,"Basi ŵankaaniile, ni twajonasile. Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chilosyo, nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila"
  26,140,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"